name: Film Soup - Aliens Invade The Beach #2
description:
Analog Photography: A film soup project by Stokanalog Bali, Indonesia.
Camera: Pentax MX (analog camera)
Lens: Pentax-M SMC 50mm f1.4
Film: Kodak Colorplus 200
Location: Bali, Indonesia
Dimensions: 1024 x 1544

Development Process: As a first step, I shot the Kodak Colorplus 200 with the Pentax MX. Then I soaked the film in vitamin C liquid and traditional Balinese wine. After that, the film was dried out for 2 weeks before it was developed at the lab.
